                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph>Also supplied in the following manufacture supplied dosage forms</paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph>DiphenhydrAMINE Hydrochloride Injection, USP in parenteral form is supplied as:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="img_97143948-4e3a-2853-e053-2995a90a3014"/>
